{"word":"G5256 - ὑπηρετέω - hypēretéō - hoop-ay-ret-eh'-o - Minister","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπηρετέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypēretéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ay-ret-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Minister</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஊழியஞ்செய், வேலைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to act as rower, to row"},{"paragraph":"2. to minister, render service"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5257 - ὑπηρέτης - hypērétēs - hoop-ay-ret'-ace/5257\">G5257</a>; to <i>be a subordinate</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>subserve:</i> - minister (unto), serve.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1311/1311\">G1311</a>, <a href=\"#/G1312/1312\">G1312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2704/2704\">G2704</a>, <a href=\"#/G5256/5256\">G5256</a>, <a href=\"#/G5257/5257\">G5257</a>, <a href=\"#/G5349/5349\">G5349</a>, <a href=\"#/G5351/5351\">G5351</a>, <a href=\"#/G861/861\">G861</a>, <a href=\"#/G862/862\">G862</a>, <a href=\"#/G90/90\">G90</a>"}]}